    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>    Storage class for recent recognitions.

    Instances of this class monitor recognitions and store them
    internally.  This class derives from the built in *list* type
    and can be accessed as if it were a normal *list* containing
    recent recognitions.  Note that an instance&apos;s contents are
    updated automatically as recognitions are received.</verbatim> </para>    </detaileddescription>
